==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wigwag
<hw>Wig"wag`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Wag</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>To signal by means of a
flag waved from side to side according to a code adopted for the
purpose.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wigwag</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Wigwag
